com.gwtplatform.mvp.client.annotations

Annotation Type Title


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface Title
    Annotation used to specify the title of a place as a string. This title is used when retrieving a place title through PlaceManager.getCurrentTitle(com.gwtplatform.mvp.client.proxy.SetPlaceTitleHandler). For more control see TitleFunction.
